We can resolve this by removing the following three lines in the AccessControlPolicyToMap method in S3AccessControlledEntity.java and removing the  call to PrivateOnlyGrantBuilder in the acl builders in AclUtils.java. My question is do we want to remove the call to PrivateOnlyGrantBuilder in all of the builders?
